üõ†Ô∏è Features for the Model

We'll include:

No. of deaths

WHO Region (one-hot encoded)

Case fatality rate

Years since first record


We'll exclude:

Country, Year, No. of cases, z-scores, and potential_outlier (either redundant or leak target).

